summary: I remember 8 year old me, listening to love story every saturday and sunday morning even though I couldn't understand any...
body:
I remember 8 year old me, listening to love story every saturday and sunday morning even though I couldn’t understand any english words.

I remember staying up all night when I was 11, so I could watch the announcement for red.

I remember 12 year old me getting bullied and listening to mean, dreaming of a better life.

I remember seeing Taylor live for the first time, giving me a reason to hold onto life.

I remember 1989 and how it also felt like a new start for me, it came out after I switched schools and I truly believed everything would be better.

I remember the 1989 tour and how much I cried to clean and how incredible I felt after that night.

I remember being filled with joy, when lwymmd came out because @taylorswift has always been such a big part in my life.

When reputation was released, I was also being happier than ever before in my life.

I am so ready to support Taylor for the rest of my life, she always had such a huge impact on my life and I don’t know where I’d be without her.

Feel free to add your story with taylor
